note: E++ HTML Reader Demo - Fetch a web page, extract its text, display it.

start program.
    say "Fetching https://example.com ...".
    fetch page "https://example.com" into raw html.
    say "Raw HTML length:", size of raw html.

    read text from html raw html into clean text.
    say "".
    say "--- Extracted Text ---".
    say clean text.
end program.
